{
  "stem": "8842.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the holidays, even then, as bad as the business was around in those days, my father used to close up his store for all seven days of Passover and the two days of Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No question about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we were a-- on a, a very religious background.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if I really understood the impact of anti-Semitism, being as I was nine, eight, you know, at that age.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because when the war broke out, I was only 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- yes, we used to hear-- going from school sometimes to take my girlfriends, we used to hear Lithuanians screaming, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Jew and not, not very pleasant words to us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or I-- yes, I used to hear from my parents telling stories to their friends what happened, certain situations.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I used to pick up that there is a anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the explanation, the real impact, what is this all about-- at that time, I don't think I really understood that deeply--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--what that meant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, not that I can-- not that I know of.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I know there was always a box at home to, to save money to send to, to Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were always going for that and going outside in the streets and collecting money for Israel through the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But otherwise, I wouldn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think they were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember my grandfather when I was about four years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember when he died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I do remember that very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gershon Zivov.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--my mother's father, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
